matrix - m*n
row major - address(A[i][j]) = Lo(base address) + [i*n + j] * w (size of data type)
column major - address(A[i][j]) = Lo(base address) + [j*m + i] * w (size of data type)

matrix n dimension A[d1][d2][d3][d4]
row major - address(A[i1][i2][i3][i4]) = Lo + [i1*d2*d3*d4 + i2*d3*d4 + i3*d4 + i4] * w
column major - address(A[i1][i2][i3][i4]) = Lo + [i4*d1*d2*d3 + i3*d1*d2 + i2*d1 + i1] * w

row major- left to right
colummn major - right to left
